<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-bottom">1.★ <strong>[C] 基部 (bottom)；基础；总部；基地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Plants are the base of the food chain. 
植物处于食物链的最底层。</p><footer>2012 四川改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He used the house as a <strong>base for</strong> his printing business.
他把这所房子作为他印刷生意的总部。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>revolutionary bases 
